sub_title: Manager for Product at SkyGeo + GRSG Chairwoman
summary:
Manager, Product at SkyGeo and Chairwoman of the Geological Remote Sensing Group (volunteer-run organisation)

Completed a PhD at Imperial college researching the identification of geotechnical hazards in London, UK using satellite InSAR, in collaboration with Thames Tideway East. Author on the CIRIA guidelines 'P3181 - Earth observation and InSAR technology for civil infrastructure'.
